reviewText: I already had "DOGFIGHTS, The Complete Series"  from the History Channel .  This DVD  contains excerpts  from that series. Disappointing!!  I had hoped I would view something new.  CN

Excellent series and DVD set! The combination of the animated mid-air battles, intercut with interviews of the actual people who who there give you a great feel for what happened that you don't get from documentaries, or live action dramas about the same battles.
